@DATABASE MarkdownViewDeskDemo
@TITLE "MarkdownViewDesk AmigaGuide Demo"
@$VER: MarkdownViewDeskDemo 0.1.5 (05.06.26)

@NODE Main "MarkdownViewDesk AmigaGuide Demo"
Welcome to a small AmigaGuide test document.

This viewer supports basic @{b}bold@{ub}, @{i}italic@{ui} and @{u}underlined@{uu} text commands.

Jump to @{"Installation" LINK Install} or @{"Notes" LINK Notes}.
@ENDNODE

@NODE Install "Installation"
1. Run install_windows.bat
2. Run run_windows.bat
3. Open .md, .guide or .diz files.

Back to @{"Main" LINK Main}.
@ENDNODE

@NODE Notes "Notes"
This is intentionally not a complete AmigaGuide v39/v40 clone.
It is meant to make typical Amiga documentation files readable in the same viewer.

@{line}
Original source / updates: github.com/zeittresor

Back to @{"Main" LINK Main}.
@ENDNODE
